\small

[1] Yu, H.-X., Duan, H., Herrmann, C., Freeman, W.T.\ \& Wu, J.\ (2025) WonderWorld: Interactive 3D scene generation from a single image. {\it arXiv preprint arXiv:2406.09394}.

[2] Paliwal, A., Zhou, X., Tsarov, A.\ \& Kalantari, N.K.\ (2024) PanoDreamer: Optimization-based single image to 360 3D scene with diffusion. {\it arXiv preprint}.

[3] Yang, L., Kang, B., Huang, Z., Zhao, Z., Xu, X., Feng, J.\ \& Zhao, H.\ (2024) Depth Anything V2. {\it arXiv preprint arXiv:2406.09414}.

[4] Yu, A., Ye, V., Tancik, M.\ \& Kanazawa, A.\ (2021) pixelNeRF: Neural radiance fields from one or few images. {\it Proceedings of the IEEE/CVF Conference on Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (CVPR)}.

[5] Suvorov, R., Logacheva, E., Mashikhin, A., Remizova, A., Ashukha, A., Silvestrov, A., Kong, N., Goka, H., Park, K.\ \& Lempitsky, V.\ (2021) Resolution-robust large mask inpainting with Fourier convolutions. {\it arXiv preprint arXiv:2109.07161}.

[6] Tochilkin, D., Pankratz, D., Liu, Z., Huang, Z., Letts, A., Li, Y., Liang, D., Laforte, C., Jampani, V.\ \& Cao, Y.-P.\ (2024) TripoSR: Fast 3D object reconstruction from a single image. {\it arXiv preprint arXiv:2403.02151}.


